<br>

<form action="/attack_with_rock" method="get">
  <label for="attack_with_rock">
    Make your move.
  </label>
  <br>
  <br>
  <input type="submit" value="Attack with rock">
</form>

<form action="/attack_with_paper" method="get">
  <br>
  <input type="submit" value="Attack with paper">
</form>

<form action="/attack_with_scissors" method="get">
  <br>
  <input type="submit" value="Attack with scissors">
</form>

(Unless your name is Edward Scissorhands, in which case attack with your hands.)
